data.description: Welcome home to a family friendly neighborhood at Baylee Preserves. 4 bedroom 3 full bath Ranch home built in 2019 with separate loft with walk-in closet and full bath. 4 spacious bedrooms with 3 walk in closets provide ample and cozy space.Unique floor plan allows for multiple gathering spots with beautiful kitchen being the heart of the home. Amazing screened in patio provides a perfect space for family gatherings and social events: 3 separate entryways, wood burning fireplace, and TV.Close to Mall of Georgia and Chateau Elan or a short trip to Lake Lanier.
